  then have "path (from_FSM M q1) q1 (left_path pC)" and "path (from_FSM M q2) q2 (right_path pC)"
    using product_path[of "from_FSM M q1" "from_FSM M q2" q1 q2 pC] by presburger+

  have "path M q1 (left_path pC)"
